{
  "text": "Motility-based diagnostics, which characterizes movement in terms of speed, frequency, and type of motion, may be developed based on current methods used for drug testing on hookworm [CITATION_1] and other helminths such as Ostertagia ostertagi, Cooperia oncophora, and Haemonchus contortus [CITATION_2] .",
